Load .qs file from a remote connection

Source: R/from_url.R
qs_from_url.Rd

Load .qs file from a remote connection

Usage

qs_from_url(url)

Arguments

url

a character url

Value

a dataframe as parsed by qs::qdeserialize()

Examples

# \donttest{
try({
  qs_from_url(
    "https://github.com/nflverse/nflverse-data/releases/download/player_stats/player_stats.qs"
  )
})
